261
0:10:41.586,000 --> 0:10:43,000
But how those puzzle pieces fit together

262
0:10:43.787,000 --> 0:10:44,000
is not immediately clear.

263
0:10:45.631,000 --> 0:10:47,000
What is clear is that this thing

264
0:10:47.927,000 --> 0:10:48,000
