284
0:11:29.202,000 --> 0:11:31,000
that they have a slightly higher risk of car accidents,

285
0:11:31.686,000 --> 0:11:33,000
and there's some evidence that people with schizophrenia

286
0:11:34.289,000 --> 0:11:36,000
